<p>All client or user login information, including emails or usernames and passwords, are securely encrypted. Login information is not shared with third parties.
   All client's or user's are responsible to keep their login information confidential. Strong, unique passwords are recommended.
</p>

<h3>Data Protection</h3>
<p>As a business, it is designed that client or user data is protected against unauthorised access, misuse, or loss. This sensitive data is restricted only to authorised personnel only.
</P>

<h3>Client or User Consent</h3>
<p>As part of the privacy policy, by using our services and providing your information, you consent to the collection and use of your information to be used by us.
</p>

<h3>Payment Information</h3>
<p>All payment information are encrypted securely only through trusted high security third-party processors.
   Transactions are stored on our servers to trace payments made for knowing all deposits made for bookings, so remaining deposit/payment is determined.
   However full card details are not stored on our servers.
</p>